name: Kenyatta Njoroge
summary:
Kenyatta Njoroge, a 32-year-old man, is currently living in Los Angeles, California. He originally comes from Nairobi, Kenya, and is fluent in English, Swahili, and Kikuyu. Kenyatta is a dedicated Nurse Practitioner in the Healthcare industry, and as a University of Nairobi graduate, he values work-life balance, family, and spirituality. As a man of Black African descent, he identifies as Christian and follows a moderate political viewpoint.

Kenyatta enjoys outdoor exercise, reading, and travelling. A Leo by zodiac signs, Kenyatta exhibits ENFJ personality traits and is a straight, monogamous individual. He has no children but wishes to become a father in the future. 

In terms of lifestyle, Kenyatta is an active individual who sometimes drinks but abstains from smoking, marijuana, and drugs. He has a pet dog. 

Kenyatta is searching for a straight life partner aged between 27 and 35, who is active, sometimes drinks but doesn't smoke or consume drugs or marijuana. His preference is that they have no children but are open to having some in the future.
